FestivalPlanner.Agenda

  • Packages that use FestivalPlanner.Agenda 
    Package Description
    FestivalPlanner.Agenda
    Contains classes relevant to data displayed in the scheduling parts of the GUI.
    FestivalPlanner.GUI.AgendaGUI
    Contains classes related to elements drawn on screen, such as objects used by JavaFX.
    FestivalPlanner.GUI.AgendaGUI.PopUpGUI
    Contains PopUps used for Object creation in the AgendaGUI software.
    FestivalPlanner.Logic
    Contains simulator logic classes.
  • Classes in FestivalPlanner.Agenda used by FestivalPlanner.Agenda 
    Class and Description
    Agenda
    Top-class of the Agenda package; contains all the information needed for the GUI.

    Contains all the data for an artist, such as the name, picture and sprite.
    Podium
    Contains all information relevant to a stage, such as the name and location.
    Show
    Contains information about a show, such as the time, name, artist and podium.
